config.name: Java client against ClickHouse ${{ matrix.clickhouse }}

env.COMMENT: Not a real token. Don't try anything funny, it won't work :)

steps.name: Check out PR
steps.run:
git fetch --no-tags --prune --progress --no-recurse-submodules --depth=1 \
  origin pull/${{ github.event.inputs.pr }}/merge:merged-pr && git checkout merged-pr

steps.name: Setup Toolchain
steps.run:
mkdir -p $HOME/.m2 \
&& cat << EOF > $HOME/.m2/toolchains.xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF8"?>
<toolchains>
  <toolchain>
    <type>jdk</type>
    <provides>
      <version>11</version>
    </provides>
    <configuration>
      <jdkHome>${{ env.JAVA_HOME }}</jdkHome>
    </configuration>
  </toolchain>
</toolchains>
EOF

steps.name: Test Java client
steps.run: mvn --also-make --batch-mode --projects clickhouse-cli-client,clickhouse-grpc-client,clickhouse-http-client -Drelease -DclickhouseVersion=${{ matrix.clickhouse }} verify

steps.name: Check out PR

  origin pull/${{ github.event.inputs.pr }}/merge:merged-pr && git checkout merged-pr

steps.name: Build and install libraries
steps.run: mvn --batch-mode --show-version --strict-checksums --threads C1 -Dmaven.wagon.rto=30000 -DskipITs install
